description.en:
Secure and Private Access to the Internet

Tutela recognises the need for privacy and has developed a secure, In-Browser encrypted desktop.
- Nobody can get their hands on your online data. 
- Enjoy online privacy and security.
- Available in 60+ Countries
- Simply Anonymous

As well as the above product, Tutela is a Cryptocurrency based off source code like DASH and PIVX. With a custom collateral structure and reward scheme, that can provide the ability for anyone to earn income through POS and MasterNoding, whilst contributing to the security of the blockchain.

Tutela's In-Browser Secure Desktop is one of a kind and designed to help users access services that are GEO Locked.
